<h2 class="post_list_item_title"><a href="https://winstonchurchill.hillsdale.edu/theologico-political-problem/" title="View full">Religion and Politics: Churchill and the Theologico-Political Problem</a></h2>
<div class="post_list_meta_unit">
<div class="date-d">17</div>
<div class="date-m">Dec</div>
<div class="date-y">2021</div>
</div>
<div class="post_list_inner_content_unit post_list_inner_content_unit_left">
<div class="authorlooplist">By <span>BEN R. CRENSHAW</span></div>
<a href="https://winstonchurchill.hillsdale.edu/theologico-political-problem/" title="Read more about Religion and Politics: Churchill and the Theologico-Political Problem">
<div class="post_list_featured_image">
<img width="770" height="300" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7" data-lazy-type="image" data-lazy-src="https://winstonchurchill.hillsdale.edu/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/Screen-Shot-2019-10-29-at-12.38.01-PM-770x300.png" class="lazy lazy-hidden img-responsive wp-post-image" alt="Crenshaw" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" /><noscript><img width="770" height="300" src="https://winstonchurchill.hillsdale.edu/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/Screen-Shot-2019-10-29-at-12.38.01-PM-770x300.png" class="img-responsive wp-post-image" alt="Crenshaw" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" /></noscript> </div>
</a>
<div class="post_list_item_excerpt">Churchill achieved a rare synthesis between the quest for philosophic truth, adherence to Christian teaching, and advancing a particular political community.</div>

<div class="post_list_cats">
<span class="post_list_cats_label">Posted in:</span>
