<h2 class="post_list_item_title"><a href="https://winstonchurchill.hillsdale.edu/churchill-jews-part-2/" title="View full">Churchill, the Jews and Israel – Part 2</a></h2>
<div class="post_list_meta_unit">
<div class="date-d">28</div>
<div class="date-m">Sep</div>
<div class="date-y">2016</div>
<div class="post_list_comment_num">
<span>1</span><i class="fa-icon-stm_icon_comment_o"></i>
</div>
</div>
<div class="post_list_inner_content_unit post_list_inner_content_unit_left">
<div class="authorlooplist">By <span>RONALD I. COHEN</span></div>
<a href="https://winstonchurchill.hillsdale.edu/churchill-jews-part-2/" title="Read more about Churchill, the Jews and Israel – Part 2">
<div class="post_list_featured_image">
<img width="770" height="300" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7" data-lazy-type="image" data-lazy-src="https://winstonchurchill.hillsdale.edu/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/WSC-and-Einstein-770x300.jpg" class="lazy lazy-hidden img-responsive wp-post-image" alt="Israel" decoding="async" /><noscript><img width="770" height="300" src="https://winstonchurchill.hillsdale.edu/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/WSC-and-Einstein-770x300.jpg" class="img-responsive wp-post-image" alt="Israel" decoding="async" /></noscript> </div>
</a>
<div class="post_list_item_excerpt">Part 2 of Ronald Cohen's address to Ambassador and Mrs. Barak and the Sir Winston Churchill Society of Ottawa at Kinneret, residence of the Ambassador, 16 June 2016.</div>

