<div class="post_list_content_unit">
<h2 class="post_list_item_title"><a href="https://winstonchurchill.hillsdale.edu/churchill-jews-israel/" title="View full">Churchill, the Jews and Israel – Part 1</a></h2>
<div class="post_list_meta_unit">
<div class="date-d">28</div>
<div class="date-m">Sep</div>
<div class="date-y">2016</div>
<div class="post_list_comment_num">
<span>2</span><i class="fa-icon-stm_icon_comment_o"></i>
</div>
</div>
<div class="post_list_inner_content_unit post_list_inner_content_unit_left">
<div class="authorlooplist">By <span>RONALD I. COHEN</span></div>
<a href="https://winstonchurchill.hillsdale.edu/churchill-jews-israel/" title="Read more about Churchill, the Jews and Israel – Part 1">
<div class="post_list_featured_image">
<img width="599" height="300" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7" data-lazy-type="image" data-lazy-src="https://winstonchurchill.hillsdale.edu/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/1921JerusalemTELAbd-599x300.jpg" class="lazy lazy-hidden img-responsive wp-post-image" alt decoding="async" /><noscript><img width="599" height="300" src="https://winstonchurchill.hillsdale.edu/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/1921JerusalemTELAbd-599x300.jpg" class="img-responsive wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" /></noscript> </div>
</a>
<div class="post_list_item_excerpt">A fresh look at Churchill and Jewry, from an address by Ronald Cohen to Ambassador and Mrs. Barak and the Sir Winston Churchill Society of Ottawa at Kinneret, residence of the Ambassador, 16 June 2016. </div>

